{{Otheruses2|the item used to cure plants|the Lunar spell|Cure Plant|the strengthened plant cure used during Garden of Tranquillity|Plant cure (Garden of Tranquillity)}}
A '''plant cure''' potion is used on diseased plants, during [[Farming]], to restore the plant to a healthy state so it continues to grow. [[Farming shop]]s sell them for 40 [[coins]] each, and [[Group of Advanced Gardeners|GAG farmer]]s at [[farming patch]]s sell them for 25 coins each. Plant cure can '''only''' be used on the same crop a single time throughout its entire life cycle.

'''Note:''' This will '''not''' work on dead plants. To ensure that your plant does not die, consider using an [[amulet of nature]] to monitor it, ''or'' pay a gardener to protect your crops automatically (gardeners will not protect herbs or flowers).

